===Etymology===
From {{L.}} {{term|tulipa|lang=la}} < {{Turk.}} {{term|tülbend|lang=tr}} < {{Pers.}} {{term|دلبند|tr=dulbend||sc=fa-Arab|lang=fa}}, also the root of {{term|turban}}; cognate with [[w:Mazandarani language|Mazandarani]] {{term|تولیپ||tulip|sc=fa-Arab|lang=mzn}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A type of flowering [[plant]], genus ''[[Tulipa]]''.
# The [[flower]] of this plant.

====Quotations====
* '''1876''' —  "[[s:The Tulip Mania|The Tulip Mania]]", ''[[w:Harper's Magazine|Harper's New Monthly Magazine]]'' No. CCCXL, April 1876, Vol. LII.
